        <p>Makes the grid "sticky," so that when you drag objects around the <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Capture">Capture</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Mimic">Frame</MadCap:conditionalText> Editor, the edge is automatically attached to the frame in relation to the nearest vertical or horizontal line of dots. Otherwise, if you do not have this option set, the position of the objects will be "loose" on the <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Capture">page</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Mimic">frame</MadCap:conditionalText>.</p>
